.TH "TRANSFORMERS_OCR" "8" "" "transformers_ocr" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
transformers_ocr \[em] screen OCR tool using Hugging Face transformers
models
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f[B]transformers_ocr\f[R] [\f[I]options\f[R]] \f[I]command\f[R]
.PP
\f[B]transformers_ocr\f[R] [\f[I]options\f[R]] \f[B]recognize\f[R]
[\f[B]\-\-image\-path\f[R] \f[I]PATH\f[R]]
.PP
\f[B]transformers_ocr\f[R] [\f[I]options\f[R]] \f[B]hold\f[R]
[\f[B]\-\-image\-path\f[R] \f[I]PATH\f[R]]
.SH DESCRIPTION
\f[B]transformers_ocr\f[R] is an OCR tool that uses Hugging Face
transformers models (manga\-ocr by default) to extract text from screen
regions.
It runs as a background listener process that communicates via a FIFO
pipe.
A screenshot is taken, optionally previewed for cropping, then sent to
the OCR model.
.PP
Supports both X11 and Wayland.
Requires a downloaded model (run \f[B]download\f[R] once after
installation).
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
\f[B]recognize\f[R] [\f[B]\-\-image\-path\f[R] \f[I]PATH\f[R]]
OCR a part of the screen.
Takes a screenshot and extracts text.
If \f[B]\-\-image\-path\f[R] is given, uses that file instead of a
screenshot.
Aliases: \f[B]ocr\f[R].
.TP
\f[B]hold\f[R] [\f[B]\-\-image\-path\f[R] \f[I]PATH\f[R]]
OCR and hold a part of the screen.
Same as \f[B]recognize\f[R] but holds the result for manual inspection.
.TP
\f[B]start\f[R] [\f[B]\-\-foreground\f[R]]
Start the background listener process.
With \f[B]\-\-foreground\f[R], runs in the current terminal.
Aliases: \f[B]listen\f[R].
.TP
\f[B]stop\f[R]
Stop the background listener.
.TP
\f[B]restart\f[R]
Stop and restart the listener.
.TP
\f[B]status\f[R]
Print listening status, platform, and model.
.TP
\f[B]download\f[R]
Download the OCR model files.
Must be run once after installation.
.TP
\f[B]purge\f[R]
Delete all downloaded model data.
Aliases: \f[B]nuke\f[R].
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\f[B]\-h\f[R], \f[B]\-\-help\f[R]
Show usage summary and exit.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
\f[B]0\f[R]
Success.
.TP
\f[B]1\f[R]
Error.
Common causes: missing dependencies, model not downloaded, screenshot
cancelled.
.TP
\f[B]130\f[R]
Interrupted (Ctrl+C).
.SH FILES
.TP
\f[B]\[ti]/.local/share/manga_ocr/*\f[R]
Downloaded model data (populated by \f[B]transformers_ocr
download\f[R]).
.SH SEE ALSO
\f[B]manga\-ocr\f[R](1)
